oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Original wills, Bache, Alberta P., 1881 December 05
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An original will of Alberta P. Bache, “residing at Benicia Arsenal, California,” dated June 2nd, 1878. Includes a document affixed with the seal of the Superior Court, State of California, Solano County, dated October 5th, 1881. Illustrates the first page of the document. Forms part of Record Group 16, Original Wills, 1780-1925.
